data.description: Bridge City beauty just 2 years old! Enjoy living in a newer construction beautiful home only minutes from schools, shopping and dining! Upon entrance, you are warmly greeted by tile floors, trending paint color with lovely light fixtures, and a bright and open floor plan seamlessly connecting the kitchen to the living room. The living room area features tray ceilings and recessed lighting with a patio door and windows that provide natural light leading to the inviting covered patio and backyard. The gas log fireplace has white tiles with a mantle that adds a warming accent to the living area. Split floor plan, with an office/desk area perfect for your computer to work from home. There is also a half bathroom convenient for guest to use when you are entertaining. The primary suite features a large area for your king size furniture. Double sinks with granite counter tops. The garden tub is accented with beautiful tiles as well as the walk-in shower. You will love the walk-in closet!
